CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper January 18, 1947, pg. 18, reads: "A Happy Celebration - Larry Alexander Givens, foster son of Atty. and Mrs. Joseph Givens of Camp Street, celebrated his sixth birthday with a gay party last week. The occasion also marked the third wedding anniversary of the honoree's foster parents. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Children, many wearing party hats, gathered around table with birthday cake, for sixth birthday of Larry Alexander Givens, in Givens home
